    "Note, as shown in Table 11, according to physiological and environmental modality, there is only a recent study in the year 2022 (From 2020-2022).",
    "Challenges and open research avenuesThere are many research challenges for emotion recognition from various modalities.",
    "These challenges can be classified as follows: First, regarding datasets, there are many datasets available for emotion recognition.",
    "Most of them are either uni-model (using only one measurement such as HR) or in the laboratory collected data.",
    "Thus, what is missing is creating real-world multi-modal datasets collected in the wild to be used as benchmarks for research experiments and comparing algorithms."
